    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/extras/e4f8d92b69a8c4997f2a75a78a295a5a.avif?t=1769883191\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/extras_big/e4f8d92b69a8c4997f2a75a78a295a5a.avif?t=1769883191 width=1560 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awaken as a prototype failsafe experiment unbeknownst as to its origin.  Tasked with purging the corruption that has befallen the highly advanced civilization.<br>Imbued with access to super computers and quantum state manipulation as a failsafe prototype, you are in a data center laboratory, the Crystal Corruption is expanding. If left unchecked, the Crystal Corruption could destroy the galaxy. The player, as a holographic construct, must seek to access and cleanse all of the data center's main quantum access ports and acquire power-ups like the Phase Warp, Magnet Boots, Power Blast, and Echo Cut to survive and confront the Core Corruption.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/extras/dd56c26e744b63653b28a0f7e690dfc3.avif?t=1769883191\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/extras_big/dd56c26e744b63653b28a0f7e690dfc3.avif?t=1769883191 width=1560 height=454 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel good fluid player movement and traversal tuned to be fun to play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Going back to the days of old, with no map system, the player must use their memory to explore</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump, shoot, explore, backtrack and collect power ups.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your movement capabilities and traverse your surroundings while enjoying satisfying, free roaming 2D Movement.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive sci-fi sound design </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore 10 themed laboratory regions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find mobility enhancements, blaster power-ups and key items to allow access to previously inaccessible areas. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot to kill a multitude of mutant threats and abominations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge traps and maneuver through various hazards.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cleanse the Corrupted access ports by manipulating entangled blocks tied to your movement to open up a clear shot to target corrupted particles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seek to find 5 quantum computer access ports for each of the 10 regions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cleanse 11 total Boss Ports</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Human crafted chip tune audio</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/extras/deab606adebb4d15343dbee5f201533b.avif?t=1769883191\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242500/extras_big/deab606adebb4d15343dbee5f201533b.avif?t=1769883191 width=1560 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
